data.meta_description: Photograph of Princess Josephine Caroline of Belgium in a half length portrait and facing the viewer. She is aged approximately 3 years old.Princess Josephine Caroline of Belgium was born on the 18th October 1872 in Brussels, Belgium, the 2nd daughter of Prince Philippe, Count of Flanders and Princess Marie of Hohenzollern-Sigmaringen. She married Prince Karl Anton on the 28th May 1894 in Brussels and together they had four children.
